sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist
    participant Dashboard as ODH Dashboard
    participant DSPA as DS Pipelines API
    participant Argo as Argo Workflows
    participant MLMeta as ml-metadata
    participant S3 as S3/MinIO
    participant Step as Pipeline Step Pod

    Note over User,Step: Workflow 2: ML Pipeline Execution

    User->>Dashboard: Login via OIDC
    User->>Dashboard: Submit pipeline run
    Dashboard->>DSPA: POST runs (via kube-rbac-proxy)

    DSPA->>Argo: Create Workflow CR
    Argo->>Argo: Reconcile: schedule step pods

    loop For each pipeline step
        Argo->>Step: Create step pod
        Step->>Step: Execute ML task
        Step->>MLMeta: Log execution metadata (gRPC/8080)
        Step->>S3: Store artifacts (HTTPS, S3 creds)
        Step-->>Argo: Step completed
    end

    Argo-->>DSPA: Workflow completed
    DSPA->>DSPA: Update run status

    User->>Dashboard: View pipeline results
    Dashboard->>DSPA: GET run details (via kube-rbac-proxy)
    DSPA-->>Dashboard: Run details + artifacts
    Dashboard-->>User: Pipeline results + visualizations
